headline.main: MACMICHAEL WARNS PALESTINE FACTIONS; High Commissioner Notes Meaning of Atlantic Charter

lead_paragraph: JERUSALEM, Jan. 2 -- Sir Harold MacMichael, High Commissioner for Palestine, warned Jews and Arabs in his New Year's message that the Atlantic Charter was a charter of freedom but that it did not mean license.
abstract: Comr H MacMichael notes meaning of Atlantic Charter
